release_note: We are excited to introduce a new section Question of the Day . In this section you will find a daily question that will help you better understand yourself and your personality. The goal of this section is to inspire you to reflect to help you focus on various aspects of your life and to increase mindfulness. Additionally we have improved calendar functionality fixed some bugs and enhanced the performance of the application!

In this version we have added notifications to ensure you don t miss your morning and evening journals as consistency is crucial if you want to achieve results and improve your life. Additionally we have fixed some errors and made the app a bit more convenient for you!
